name: Lester Oxford Performance Polo
description:
The Lester Oxford polo is a love-at-first-feel shirt. Spun from an innovative process that turns eucalyptus pulp into yarn, the Lester delivers an exceptionally soft feel that’s sure to become a favorite.
“The Softest Thing You’ll Ever Have on Your Skin” 
We were blown away the first time we felt this fabric, and we couldn’t wait to use it to make a shirt that looks amazing on you, will keep you cool and dry, and is built to last for many years. 
Let’s talk about The Lester Performance Polo. 
The magic of The Lester is in the fabric. It’s the first shirt we’ve introduced that’s primarily Modal, with a little sprinkle of polyester thrown in.  
What’s Modal, you ask? It’s a plant-derived fabric in the rayon family, which means it has a soft, silky feel when you touch it.  
The science of Modal fabric is pretty extraordinary, and it yields apparel that outperforms in the areas of stretch, absorbance, durability, and comfort.  
Crafted to deliver an exceptional look 
For The Lester Polo we used Modal to create a signature Oxford fabric, combining colored threads with white threads to deliver a soft, sophisticated look.   
The fabric is noticeably different to the eye. Side-by-side with a pima cotton polo or classic performance polo, the sophisticated look of The Lester is eye-catching in just the right way.  
Engineered for durability 
Not to get all science-y on you, but it’s worth taking just a moment to talk about the benefits you get from how our unique Modal fabric is made.  
Long story short, Modal fabric goes through a more extensive production process than similar fibers, which makes the final product stronger, lighter, and breathable. 
This means you get a shirt that maintains its refined look and is less susceptible to wear-and-tear than some of the other items in your closet. 
Feeling is believing 
It’s one thing to make an innovative fabric, but it’s another thing to make a shirt that you love to wear. The Lester Polo shares the classic fit, crisp collars, and ease-of-care you’ll find with our other polos.  
It’s hard to capture what makes The Lester Polo special in an email or blog post. We say “feeling is believing” with The Lester, so go ahead and choose your new Lester Polo now or find your new Lester at one of our valued retail partners near you. name: Lester Oxford Performance Polo
description:
The Lester Oxford polo is a love-at-first-feel shirt. Spun from an innovative process that turns eucalyptus pulp into yarn, the Lester delivers an exceptionally soft feel that’s sure to become a favorite.
“The Softest Thing You’ll Ever Have on Your Skin” 
We were blown away the first time we felt this fabric, and we couldn’t wait to use it to make a shirt that looks amazing on you, will keep you cool and dry, and is built to last for many years. 
Let’s talk about The Lester Performance Polo. 
The magic of The Lester is in the fabric. It’s the first shirt we’ve introduced that’s primarily Modal, with a little sprinkle of polyester thrown in.  
What’s Modal, you ask? It’s a plant-derived fabric in the rayon family, which means it has a soft, silky feel when you touch it.  
The science of Modal fabric is pretty extraordinary, and it yields apparel that outperforms in the areas of stretch, absorbance, durability, and comfort.  
Crafted to deliver an exceptional look 
For The Lester Polo we used Modal to create a signature Oxford fabric, combining colored threads with white threads to deliver a soft, sophisticated look.   
The fabric is noticeably different to the eye. Side-by-side with a pima cotton polo or classic performance polo, the sophisticated look of The Lester is eye-catching in just the right way.  
Engineered for durability 
Not to get all science-y on you, but it’s worth taking just a moment to talk about the benefits you get from how our unique Modal fabric is made.  
Long story short, Modal fabric goes through a more extensive production process than similar fibers, which makes the final product stronger, lighter, and breathable. 
This means you get a shirt that maintains its refined look and is less susceptible to wear-and-tear than some of the other items in your closet. 
Feeling is believing 
It’s one thing to make an innovative fabric, but it’s another thing to make a shirt that you love to wear. The Lester Polo shares the classic fit, crisp collars, and ease-of-care you’ll find with our other polos.  
It’s hard to capture what makes The Lester Polo special in an email or blog post. We say “feeling is believing” with The Lester, so go ahead and choose your new Lester Polo now or find your new Lester at one of our valued retail partners near you. Turtleson performance polos are designed for style but built for action and will carry you through work and play.  Our polo is known for its fit, fabric and construction. Its superior Self-Fabric Collar is designed specifically to maintain shape and features built-in stays. 
The Cooper is one of our most traditional designs and shows brilliant depth of color. Self-Fabric Collar 3-Button Placket Short Sleeve Moisture-Wicking, Quick-Dry Finish 92% Polyester, 8% Spandex

name: Axl Quarter-Zip Pullover
description: The Axl brings a fun citrus pattern to our lightest-weight quarter-zip fabric. Ideal for a breezy day on the boat or ice cold beers at the raw bar. Moisture-Wicking, Quick-Dry Fabric Quarter-Zip Collar with Logo Zipper Pull Long Sleeve 62% Polyester, 27% Poly Graphene, 11% Spandex
